{"tid":404182,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"中國女獨走街頭測反應　印男疑自摸下體解慾","createTime":"2017-09-17T23:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T00:14:26.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"230a2ae283ec051609ee9726190241da8f6ae6dc","tid":404182,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:55:21.000Z","msg":"Joke TV為一個專門做社會實驗的頻道，策劃人Joke最近於印度性犯罪率極高的城市新德里進行了一項街頭實驗，測試印男遇到一名皮膚白皙的女子的反應，結果竟有男子疑在光天化日之下，在路過女子後自摸下體「解慾」！<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597.jpg&h=b77101d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYouTube截圖<br />\n <br />\nJoke邀請一名短髮中國籍女子進行印度該項社會實驗，女子當日的衣著與當地女子的衣著大有不同，在透視裝的底下，底衫若隱若現，再搭配上一條稍露大腿的裙，背上斜肩袋，不時研究下當地地圖，又影下相，像一名遊客走在印度街頭，但得到的「回頭率」極度高！<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_2.jpg&h=cca3cfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_4.jpg&h=0accc634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_3.jpg&h=0009cf2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_5.jpg&h=c666c6aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子走到人多的地方以便進行測試，不少印男眼甘甘望到實，與友人交頭接耳，加上露齒的竊笑，不禁令網民覺得可怕。印男又會打量女子，即使女子只是普通地查閱地圖，都會惹來旁人的眼光，更有印男在「觀察」完女子後，疑似自摸下體，但就有網民認為男子只是下體痕，覺得不舒適才當街做出這個行為。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_6.jpg&h=48e9c149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_7.jpg&h=8443c1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然整個街頭實驗過程中沒有發生任何意外，但Joke仍在影片最後提醒網民「不要獨自做這個實驗」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/09/20170915_pl_%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6_%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F09%2F20170915_pl_%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6_%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597_8.jpg&h=5d63d37b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民認為該項實驗太過危險，又形容女子獨自出現在印度街頭就像「待宰的羔羊」。但亦有人認為印男只是過於好奇，更指自己曾經亦走在印度街頭，印度女性亦會眼甘甘望住自己。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/2414155-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E7%8D%A8%E8%B5%B0%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%B8%AC%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89-%E5%8D%B0%E7%94%B7%E7%96%91%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E8%A7%A3%E6%85%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9-plastic-post%2F2414155-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2587%2589-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2585%25BE&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7a1674ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/2414155-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E7%8D%A8%E8%B5%B0%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%B8%AC%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89-%E5%8D%B0%E7%94%B7%E7%96%91%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94%E8%A7%A3%E6%85%BE</a>"},{"pid":"4d7d41e2ea18390589e55b506a7cf97846144968","tid":404182,"uid":146031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:56:54.000Z","msg":"五十步笑百步"},{"pid":"7589721d3988ebfbc6bfb5e8b8626f09dc7631e6","tid":404182,"uid":13207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:12:34.000Z","msg":"阿嬸"},{"pid":"4793df326760bd62e23ddf3f80f6e39224594fe0","tid":404182,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"男人行過佢地都會望，因為少外國人去"}]}